people died of starvation,

00:29:20.320 --> 00:29:21.260 align:middle line:90%
literally millions.

00:29:21.260 --> 00:29:23.509 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Multiply
that times 10 or 100.

00:29:23.509 --> 00:29:24.050 align:middle line:90%
>>FELIX: Yes.

00:29:24.050 --> 00:29:26.450 align:middle line:10%
But the thing is is
that back then, they

00:29:26.450 --> 00:29:30.440 align:middle line:10%
didn't have the kind of
transportation we have now.

00:29:30.440 --> 00:29:35.440 align:middle line:10%
So back then they had to
depend on local sources

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:36.600 align:middle line:10%
for their food.

00:29:36.600 --> 00:29:39.890 align:middle line:10%
Today we can bring in food
from all over the world,

00:29:39.890 --> 00:29:41.840 align:middle line:10%
or the various places can.

00:29:41.840 --> 00:29:44.024 align:middle line:84%
Back then, they had no
way of being warned.

00:29:44.024 --> 00:29:45.440 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: But if
you can't travel--

00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:46.065 align:middle line:90%
>>FELIX: If you can't travel--

